==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lampless
<hw>Lamp"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Being without a lamp, or without
light; hence, being without appreciation; dull.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your ladies' eyes are <qex>lampless</qex> to that virtue.</q>
<rj><qau>Beau. & Fl.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lamplight</ent>⟦br⟧
